{"type":null,"faqId":32806,"title":"超级夜景拍照和普通手机的长时间曝光有什么区别","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body7991722\"><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033750059__p23567568\">普通手机的长曝光（M档）是纯粹的物理曝光技术拍摄，对手持要求较高，而且由于宽容度限制，容易出现亮处过曝等场景。此外由于传感器以及ISP的限制，曝光时间不会很长，一般手机只能到8秒钟，极少有超过30秒钟。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033750059__p10781521\">超级夜景使用了更先进的算法技术，通过拍摄多帧合成来获取照片，拍摄时间理论上没有限制，通过支持更长时间曝光，比较黑的场景能够拍出来，甚至人眼看不清的也能拍出来，此外通过算法加强处理，照片效果和降噪效果更好，通过拍摄后重调白平衡等技术来确保可以获得更好的效果。</p></div></body>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0033750059","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748410000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10,PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-TL11H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":6,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"超级夜景与长曝光的区别,超级夜景是长时间曝光吗,","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}